* Program description:
* This method changes the Header of a given HU
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*

*=======================================================================
* Declaration/Initialization
*=======================================================================

  DATA:
        lo_wm_packing     TYPE REF TO /scwm/cl_wm_packing.


